United Technologies Research Center (UTRC) is an internationally recognized R&amp;D organization that performs innovative research through a "growth through innovation" mission in support of the commercial and aerospace business units of United Technologies Corporation (UTC). The operating units of UTC include Pratt &amp; Whitney, Sikorsky Aircraft, Otis Elevators, Carrier, Hamilton-Sundstrand aerospace products, UTC Power, including UTC Fuel Cells and combined heat and power products, and Chubb security products and services. UTRC partners with the UTC business units to impact organic growth of the Corporation through disruptive innovation that is manifested in both new products and new processes. To realize the mission of impact through innovation, UTRC also partners with the best research organizations in the world providing opportunities for external collaboration. The UTRC operation in China supports this mission by creating and deploying the capability to conduct virtual product design utilizing models of new UTC products and processes and using these models to conduct rigorous conceptual and preliminary design.
美国联合技术公司-UnitedTechnologies Corp.（UTC）是世界最大的制造公司之一，主要为全球航空航天和建筑业提供高技术的产品和服务。UTC旗下共有7个子公司和1个直属研究机构.截至2003年UTC的全球雇员人数已达205,700。2004年公司名列财富500强排行榜第141位。自2001年以来UTC已连续4年被美国财富杂志评选为美国航空技术业\'最令人尊敬的公司\'。公司曾被美国劳动部授予公司"最佳工作场所"奖。
联合技术研究中心（UTRC）是直属UTC的研究机构。旨在为满足公司所属企业现在和将来的技术需求而进行技术研究和开发。联合技术研究中心在许多重要的技术领域中,占据全球领先地位。联合技术研究中心（中国）有限公司（UTRC China）于1997年设立于上海，是中心在海外设立的唯一的独资公司,现诚聘以下专业人才.
UTC BUSINESS UNITS with Products
Carrier heating and air conditioning systems
United Technologies Fire &amp; Security
Hamilton Sundstrand aerospace and industrial systems
Otis elevators and escalators
Pratt &amp; Whitney aircraft engines
Sikorsky helicopters
UTC Power
一经录用公司将提供具有竞争力的薪酬和完善的培训。
